statement.p:
Which of the following expressions are proportions?

\dfrac{3}{x}=\dfrac{8}{15}	

\dfrac{v}{9}-\dfrac{12}{5}

\dfrac{w}{6}+\dfrac{2}{5}=\dfrac{3}{2}

\dfrac{2.6}{m}=\dfrac{m}{1.6}

